{"tid":1363200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄉黑係721已先動手傷害平民及義士，727如義士有行動都不屬於「先動手」而是「還手」","createTime":"2019-07-25T06:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T06:39:01.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1c39e65e99ca190f20aecee2b1da8a6272f3097d","tid":1363200,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"首先我唔知727會係點, 亦唔係叫任何人點做或做D乜<br />\n總之自己諗, 現場自決<br />\n<br />\n但要搞清楚一個CONCEPT先：<br />\n成村人話727係唔要「首先出手」，被鄉黑打先「還手」<br />\n事實係： 鄉黑係721已先動手傷害平民及義士<br />\n721及727是兩個日期, 但係連貫及同一件事嚟<br />\n<br />\n因此，邏輯上，<br />\n就算到727當日，義士首先進行任何行動，都係屬於鄉黑係先動手後的還手行動<br />\n<br />\n對於「先攻」及「還手」, CONCEPT唔該搞清楚！<br />\n<br />\n成班人將721同727分割？<br />\n同一件事嚟架嘛！<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以將上一分鐘同下一分鐘分割？"},{"pid":"26bb3e1a9bc371a4f1a2f22a66dec488c120dbec","tid":1363200,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:00:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727對準鄉黑</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n恐怖份子巢穴：<br />\n元朗南邊圍福德堂 (人數不明) + 天水圍廈村 (200人) + 廈溪 (人數不明)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/j_bFtUs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fj_bFtUs_1200x0.png&h=f19a4595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i1.wp.com/tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMAGE-2019-07-22-034503.jpg?fit=1280%2C852&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FIMAGE-2019-07-22-034503.jpg%3Ffit%3D1280%252C852%26ssl%3D1&h=144559cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180303/photo/bkn-20180303174105327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180303182522\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180303%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180303174105327-0303_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180303182522&h=b7b43767&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.postimg.cc/d1RbdsTg/yl-1-2-gate.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fd1RbdsTg%2Fyl-1-2-gate.jpg&h=53120000&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當日疑接載白衫鄉黑的車牌：<br />\n<br />\nVW 9089<br />\nWZ 7266<br />\nNT 21<br />\nVL 9886<br />\nTM 790<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n元朗鄉黑生意主要圍繞水邊圍嘅無牌酒吧做毒品飯堂，元朗嘅有牌酒吧就收保護費。同樂街一帶嘅色情場所，炮仗坊一帶嘅賭檔，仲有元朗所有嘅機鋪，佢地都有份，搞射魚，比人賭錢，基本上佢地生意分佈就係咁。<br />\n<br />\n請大家幫手光復元朗當日行動，配合記者及公眾輿論將黑勢力竇口公佈比全香港人知。<br />\n<br />\n(1) 元朗V Zone<br />\n- 元朗西裕街足彬大廈地下6號舖<br />\n經常有黑幫人士聚集<br />\n<br />\n(2) 元朗大三元得勝號<br />\n- 元朗炮仗坊16號地下<br />\n黑幫人士經營，經常有黑幫人士聚集<br />\n<br />\n(3) 元朗Magic Club<br />\n- 元朗安樂路59-61號永興大廈地下1號舖<br />\n老闆為黑幫骨幹人物，內有睇場及黑幫人士集結<br />\n<br />\n(4) 元朗歡樂吧 Enjoy Pub<br />\n- 元朗安樂路61號永興大廈地下3-4號舖<br />\n老闆為黑幫骨幹人物，經常有黑幫聚集<br />\n<br />\n(5) 元朗勝和無牌酒吧<br />\n- 水邊圍屏昌徑媽橫路21-23號鋪 (前門不開閘，入口只有後巷鐵門)<br />\n經常有黑幫骨幹人士在內聚集，內藏武器、 毒品；只要進入後巷，有好幾處有cctv既鐵門，都係佢地既鐵竇<br />\n<br />\n(6) 元朗銀湖芬蘭浴室桑拿<br />\n- 元朗合益路17-51號地庫<br />\n與黑幫人士有關聯，不少黑幫人士聚集<br />\n<br />\n(7) 元朗at restaurant &amp; bar<br />\n- 元朗西菁街23號富達廣場地下31號舖<br />\n經常有黑幫人士聚集，內有職員為黑幫人士<br />\n<br />\n(8) 元朗feverbar (有兩間，另一間係旁間位置)<br />\n- 新界元朗媽廟路幸福樓15號地鋪（fever 1)<br />\n- 新界元朗媽廟路幸福樓13號地鋪（fever 2)<br />\n黑幫人士聚集地，內有職員為黑幫人士<br />\n<br />\n(9) 蛇王如<br />\n- 元朗安寧路屏會街屏昌徑紫荊樓地下一號 A<br />\n電話： 2478 1428<br />\n經常有黑幫人士聚集，內有職員為黑幫人士<br />\n<br />\n元朗炮仗坊 好彩麻雀娛樂公司 (沒有圖片)<br />\n- 元朗炮仗坊16號號地下<br />\n為黑幫人士經營，黑幫收入來源之一，極多黑幫人士聚集<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/R0xpoJg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR0xpoJg.jpg&h=5dac27a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"490f959a2bdfd7db5077eefc760f13af70d3a2bc","tid":1363200,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"對準黑社會、黑警、黑議員三類人，不作無差別攻擊"},{"pid":"3b05fbbcdd16dd026090aba04fac9ce39121e902","tid":1363200,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"你到時候點知要打邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93049b526cd918683fefa50d2da5a87158a9974c","tid":1363200,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b05fbbcdd16dd026090aba04fac9ce39121e902","tid":1363200,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T10:18:00.000Z","msg":"你到時候點知要打邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:10:17.000Z","msg":"點會唔知?<br />\n<br />\n唔關事既一早走晒<br />\n<br />\n拿晒武器企出嚟, 一眼睇就知鄉黑<br />\n<br />\n起晒底有晒樣<br />\n<br />\n你盲?"},{"pid":"92ce6ed8bf8e828db734e8d86f5b7354cf456ab8","tid":1363200,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"490f959a2bdfd7db5077eefc760f13af70d3a2bc","tid":1363200,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:10:00.000Z","msg":"對準黑社會、黑警、黑議員三類人，不作無差別攻擊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:10:27.000Z","msg":"起晒底有晒樣"},{"pid":"a74a7d9912efe0ef7890ec85efbeeec7a03fa2a7","tid":1363200,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:12:03.000Z","msg":"721 = 偷襲珍珠港<br />\n727 = 杜立德炸東京<br />\n<br />\n同一件事, 同一個世界大戰, 同一個太平洋戰爭嚟<br />\n<br />\n點可能分割去計?"},{"pid":"21970b000a8f6ab54e9209cab040feaa1ec750aa","tid":1363200,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:17:52.000Z","msg":"「還手唔係發生同一日就會reset無數再計過」係邊條粉腸發明既concept oncept 嚟??<br />\n<br />\n係咪CLS??<br />\n<br />\ninsane?  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c58688c7f48f0d32fa5dbeb1ed5954cd90f15bc","tid":1363200,"uid":275189,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime